    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>ABOUT</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master 100+ Spells — No two runs play the same. Battle brutal bosses, dodge insane bullet hell, and dominate The Spire! Customize your hero with Pets, Perks, Classes, Cosmetics and <strong>MORE</strong>!  <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>CONQUER EACH FLOOR</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, Blast, and Dodge your way up the tower with over 100+ unique spells. Each spell has a unique form and plays differently than the last. Whether you're freezing enemies with a glacial spike, or hurling meteors down on your foes, master them to melt through enemies and climb even higher.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/f700591b00b68bbc30a7d0b0268791d2.poster.avif?t=1769010898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/f700591b00b68bbc30a7d0b0268791d2.webm?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/f700591b00b68bbc30a7d0b0268791d2.mp4?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>BECOME SUPER POWERFUL</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading a spell isn’t just a stat boost, it’s a transformation. Each upgrade reshapes the spell into something stronger, flashier, and way more fun. With most spells evolving across three tiers, you’re free to go 'all-in' on your favorites, and unleash their full potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/6da6e4b029b39380135a7c1e1c9bc577.poster.avif?t=1769010898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/6da6e4b029b39380135a7c1e1c9bc577.webm?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/6da6e4b029b39380135a7c1e1c9bc577.mp4?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong> <u>CUSTOMIZE YOUR BUILD</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's a new class, pet, perk, mask, or cosmetic, there are thousands of combinations to make each and every run feel fresh.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/589faeafd3af621d131bd2d1c333f32e.poster.avif?t=1769010898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/589faeafd3af621d131bd2d1c333f32e.webm?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/589faeafd3af621d131bd2d1c333f32e.mp4?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>DISCOVER</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock various NPC's that aid you on your path. Seek out forgotten chambers, sacred masks, and powerful boss runes, each one pulsing with power and waiting to reshape your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/029949c21f69154c4b1acc553f5a3d1c.poster.avif?t=1769010898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/029949c21f69154c4b1acc553f5a3d1c.webm?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/029949c21f69154c4b1acc553f5a3d1c.mp4?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FACE THE CHALLENGE</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the guardians of the tower in EPIC boss battles! Do you have what it takes to come out on top?<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/0e80c747e3f9dd6268e58d09f11e4201.poster.avif?t=1769010898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/0e80c747e3f9dd6268e58d09f11e4201.webm?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189770/extras/0e80c747e3f9dd6268e58d09f11e4201.mp4?t=1769010898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Features:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way, with multiple unique classes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ distinct spells.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Dozens of meta-progression perks, pets, and NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Spell Upgrade System that <i><u>isn't</u></i> just a number increase.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover NPC's in the tower that will help you face even greater threats!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loads of Cosmetics that unlock via achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find dozens of masks each with a special unique ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Gacha <i><u>without</u></i> microtransactions. (In-game currency only)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss perks! - After defeating a boss, choose an additional perk to help you climb higher. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty options to tailor each run to your skill and mood.</p></li></ul>",
